Package: apus
Type: Package
Title: Advises an optimal fertilizer mix for a farm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sven", 
           family = "Verweij",
           email = "sven.verweij@nmi-agro.nl",
           role = c("aut","cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-5573-3952')))
Description: apus optimizes the fertilizer mix for a farm based on the nutrient 
    requirements, legal norms, cultivation response curves, available fertilizers 
    and tries to archieve the best economic result within the provided boundaries.
